<document>

  <properties>
    <title>ArgoUML AndroMDA Module</title>
    <author email="rastaman@tigris.org">Ludovic Maitre</author>
  </properties>

  <body>
    <section name="Overview">
      <p>
        This is an ArgoUML module which allow the user to run 
        <a href="http://maven.apache.org">Maven</a> on an 
        <a href="http://www.andromda.org/">AndroMDA</a> model from inside ArgoUML. 
     </p>
     <p>
        The module also provide features for setting environment variables before 
        running  Maven and to create new AndroMDA project via a wizard dialog.        
      </p>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>
